<bibRefCitation id="F8184B6C136F5415FF4AFF5C77C4E18E" box="[238,418,222,244]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" refId="ref34761" refString="Li, Z. Z. &amp; Wang, L. M. (1994) A new genus and three new species of the tribe Evacanthini (Insecta: Homoptera: Cicadellidae) with a key to the genera and a list of species occurring in China. Journal of Natural History, 28, 375 - 382. https: // doi. org / 10.1080 / 00222939400770161" type="journal article">Li &amp; Wang, 1994</bibRefCitation>
